{"tid":839055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亮劍] 不滿瑞典電視台辱華　內地網民揚言抵制IKEA：以後不去宜家睡覺","createTime":"2018-09-27T15:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T15:33:58.000Z","uid":31744,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6456f45942a1c6a70a10681efb1ee2fe7506b073","tid":839055,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"瑞典電視台（SVT）近日在節目「瑞典新聞」播出短片，諷刺中國遊客隨地大便等，結果被內地多個官媒包括央視、新華社、《環球時報》等，紛紛高調譴責辱華，外交部與旅遊部甚至對瑞典發出旅遊警告。事件引發不少網民揚言要抵制瑞典品牌「IKEA宜家家居」，不過未有做足功課的網民，可能不知道原來IKEA在中國賣的商品，有80%都是中國製造。<br />\n<br />\n在早前瑞典電視台播出的短片中，除諷刺中國遊客隨地大便外，亦指他們如廁後不洗手、中國人食狗肉、是「種族主義者」等，事後引起中國官媒大篇幅報道斥瑞典「辱華」，不少愛國網民亦一窩蜂湧到宜家的微博留言炮轟，指不滿瑞典歧視中國，遂發起抵制行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">揚言「以後再也不去宜家睡覺」</span>、「在瑞典電視台不道歉之前，我是不會再買宜家的任何東西」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/231744_7f0c2170449c28cfe5225995af4d3c7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F231744_7f0c2170449c28cfe5225995af4d3c7a.png&h=92181e7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e40f36fbdb36071d148ffefe2a2c3bf494c8889","tid":839055,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b59456c488ca576aee8fe9b875e4661ef35c1c","tid":839055,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔買，但抄晒人啲款山寨貨扮原創扼人"},{"pid":"6d62378195b31484e48f3920e6d094516c57c8d5","tid":839055,"uid":182499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"覺得好曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d15060f04a6a37a59ce77c99724d0994c919ea8","t